Package digital.ivan.lightchain.core.prompt

package digital.ivan.lightchain.core.prompt
  • Class
    Description
    IPromptTemplateProvider
    The IPromptTemplateProvider interface defines methods that allow a prompt template to be provided, including a list of required placeholders, and a validation method for these placeholders.
    KeyConsts
    Enumeration representing a set of constants used as keys in the prompt template.
    SimplePromptBuilder
    The SimplePromptBuilder class is used for building prompts from templates provided by an IPromptTemplateProvider.
